{
  "stem": "19690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my father-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --put his hand on my head and gave me the priestly blessing-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --which he would have done every holiday and every Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I knew this was that last time that it would ever happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And as he and other fathers did that, the guard walked away, turned around, and cried just like I'm crying.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The reason I'm mentioning it is that as the roll was called, there were several children that were sick and the committee had people standing by.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And every time a name wasn't answered, someone else jumped into the bus.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so we had extra people in the bus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The guard didn't pay attention.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we got out of the camp, the bus was loaded, two buses were loaded, and we were taken out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were maybe a mile away from camp when the buses suddenly stopped, the doors opened up, and there were others-- youngsters, two in each bus-- that came in.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They had been tied to the bottom of the buses in camp and had ridden out on the buses to escape.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "These were 18-, 19-year-olds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they came into the buses and then we went on to Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were taken to Hotel Bonaparte, which is another one of the internment hotels in Marseille.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were taken there and left there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ones that had been hidden in the buses were left off in the city and were met by underground people and they left immediately from there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Hotel Bonaparte, we were with some older people who had been left behind when all of the other women and children were taken to Les Milles.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
